{"tid":629102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"眾籌查UGL案　5日獲167萬","createTime":"2018-04-14T12:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T12:42:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"46b846e824b8cc15fbb97039fcde46cafea6cc14","tid":629102,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T12:12:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361238?_ga=2.111199876.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361238%3F_ga%3D2.111199876.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=CBOHiE6ZMgMxqOj8rowLsUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=472f32ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361238%3F_ga%3D2.111199876.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=2aa8aaa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361238?_ga=2.111199876.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌查UGL案　5日獲167萬<br />\n<br />\n5.1K<br />\n要聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180414/large/a0605a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180414%2Flarge%2Fa0605a.gif&h=beba4bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主黨發起「天下為公」眾籌計劃，目標籌集200萬港元繼續追查前特首梁振英涉收取UGL公司5,000萬的事件，截至昨晚11時已籌得逾167萬元（圖），距離成功達標差不足兩成。民主派政黨繼續呼籲市民捐款，發起人之一、已故立法局議員吳明欽女兒吳思諾就拍片指，參與事件是延續爸爸「追求公義、堅持到底」的精神，呼籲市民支持計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吳思諾拍片籲捍衞公義<br />\n<br />\n民主黨周一公佈透過「天下為公」計劃眾籌200萬元，追查梁振英收取UGL公司5,000萬的事，事件至今只有5天，但已籌得逾167萬元，佔目標金額超過八成。發起人之一、立法會議員林卓廷指，因為條例所限未能安排實體的捐款渠道，惟對目前的進度感滿意，他們現正擬訂工作計劃，只要眾籌達標就會即展開工作。<br />\n<br />\n前晚首條影片已經上載到「天下為公」的fb，主角是大律師吳思諾，吳指，她認識的爸爸是「追求公義、堅持到底」的人，更因此而被襲擊受傷。她眼見梁振英涉UGL案至今仍然未被檢控，質疑「法律之下，有人比其他人更平等」。她在片中呼籲捍衞公義的市民，參與「天下為公」眾籌計劃，繼續追究梁振英。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕"},{"pid":"36d648172ca9fb1bfe749513f64fac33418e8c37","tid":629102,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T12:14:27.000Z","msg":"又有人科水 真係fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18ffd867e665165f0826e3adf7337713a1bb7a8","tid":629102,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"就比一舊水 等睇689仆街"},{"pid":"72a149715d245e2303398d4d68283b850509c2e4","tid":629102,"uid":22422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a18ffd867e665165f0826e3adf7337713a1bb7a8","tid":629102,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"就比一舊水 等睇689仆街"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T12:19:44.000Z","msg":"你都賺咗steam幾萬蚊<br />\n唔爭在"},{"pid":"eb4faf35f737e5d1c2efdee724801287786199ed","tid":629102,"uid":17765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a18ffd867e665165f0826e3adf7337713a1bb7a8","tid":629102,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"就比一舊水 等睇689仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T12:21:21.000Z","msg":"緊係Steam仆街先<br />\n佢驚畀你告到破產<br />\n對腳震撚過貓王<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6495b7131492f716b0c7ad9ef47b12a2e87d52","tid":629102,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72a149715d245e2303398d4d68283b850509c2e4","tid":629102,"uid":22422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a18ffd867e665165f0826e3adf7337713a1bb7a8","tid":629102,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"就比一舊水 等睇689仆街"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T12:19:44.000Z","msg":"你都賺咗steam幾萬蚊<br />\n唔爭在"},"citedBy":0,"repl